		{"id":"b8c112016cbbd721","type":"group","x":6940,"y":-1433,"width":2220,"height":1576,"label":"REVISITING PAGES - i  worked from page 4 to page 5 to page 3 to page 2  here. Things became more clear/specific in that order"},
